# Backend Architecture Standards

This project follows structured Python architecture principles.

## Framework Conventions

Use the project's established framework (Django, FastAPI, Flask, or similar).

Follow the framework's conventions for:

- Routing / URL configuration
- Middleware
- Dependency injection (FastAPI) or signals (Django)
- Configuration management

Do not mix frameworks вЂ” stick to one per project.

